					<div id="mw-content-text" class="mw-body-content"><div class="mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output" lang="en" dir="ltr"><div class="shortdescription nomobile noexcerpt noprint searchaux" style="display:none">US Supreme Court justice from 1986 to 2016</div>
<div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">"Scalia" redirects here. For the surname, see <a href="/wiki/Scalia_(surname)" title="Scalia (surname)">Scalia (surname)</a>.</div>
<p class="mw-empty-elt">



</p>
