<li id="cite_note-11"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-11">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Senators <a href="/wiki/Barry_Goldwater" title="Barry Goldwater">Barry Goldwater</a> and <a href="/wiki/Jake_Garn" title="Jake Garn">Jake Garn</a> were not present for the confirmation.</span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-111"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-111">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Scalia was joined by Justices Thomas, Souter, Breyer, and Ginsburg.</span>
</li>
</ol></div></div>
